• Deric Williamson, Cent. Crossing 
Passed for 388 yards and five touchdowns and added a rushing score in a 48-42 overtime win over Dublin Coffman. 
• Gunnar Gregory, Centerburg 
Passed for 360 yards and two touchdowns in a 35-28 loss to Fredericktown.

Had nine receptions for 244 yards and four touchdowns in the win over Canal Winchester.
